steps.name: Then I should see ACCOUNT CREATED and click Continue button
assert expected <b> to contain Account Created!
Then I should see Logged in as username at the top
assert expected <a> to contain Logged in as Mellie
When I add products to the cart
And I click the Cart button
Then I should see the cart page displayed
assert expected <li.active> to contain Shopping Cart
When I click Proceed To Checkout
Then I should see delivery address matches registration info
assert expected Mr. Mellie Snow to equal Mr. Mellie Snow
assert expected Shapla 2 to equal Shapla 2
assert expected Rajsahi Rajsahi\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1400 to equal Rajsahi Rajsahi\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1400
assert expected India to equal India
And I should see billing address matches registration info
assert expected [ <li.address_address1.address_address2>, 2 more... ] to contain Shapla 2
When I click the Delete Account button
Then I should see ACCOUNT DELETED and click Continue button
assert expected <b> to contain Account Deleted!
